QuestData.Title: The Battle for the West
QuestData.Description: Our base is barely built and already the Iron Horde sets up defenses against us. Still the plan worked and we fight on two fronts.$b$bI have received word that Exarch Maladaar has finally breached the western gates as well, but is bogged down in a pitched battle. You should go see the situation for yourself.
QuestData.LogDescription: Go to the Iron Front and speak with Exarch Maladaar.
QuestData.RewardText: Now you see what we face here. We will keep as much pressure here as we can so your base can remain free to attack all over the jungle.

Objectives.Objective: Talk to Thann to fly to the Iron Front
